=head1 DESCRIPTION

An object that describes the state of the canonical name (CNAME)
records that are automatically added by Lightsail to the DNS of the
domain to validate domain ownership.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Code => Str

The status code for the automated DNS record creation.

Following are the possible values:

=over

=item *

C<SUCCEEDED> - The validation records were successfully added.

=item *

C<STARTED> - The automatic DNS record creation has started.

=item *

C<FAILED> - The validation record addition failed.

=back



=head2 Message => Str

The message that describes the reason for the status code.



